Description: GrTiPy
        =======
        
        General Relativity toolbox in Python
        based on SymPy (python library for symbolic mathematics).
        
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        GrTiPy depends on:
        
        * Python (version >=2.6)
        * SymPy (version >=7.3)
        * IPython (version >=1.1.0)
        
        IPython notebook isn't required but it makes it easier to work with complex 
        mathematical formulas.
        
        To install GrTiPy, simply run
        
            $ python setup.py install
        
        or
        
            $ pip install GrTiPy
        
        
        Documentation and usage
        -----------------------
        
        docs/GrTiPy-tutorial.ipynb
        Example/____.py
        
